title: Ask HN: What degree should I be getting?
text:
I don’t have a degree currently but I’ve worked as a developer for about two years now. I think getting a degree in something would fulfill me.

I am aware of the fact that getting a degree is not required in this industry because most of it can be self taught, but I want to get a degree for my personal benefit, I think I would grow much more.

Is a computer science degree worth it? What about computer engineer or electrical enginner?

Which would I get the most out of? Whar are your thoughts?
